79
00:03:08.585 --> 00:03:12.665
Y ensancharon sobre mí su boca, dijeron, ea,

80
00:03:12.665 --> 00:03:15.225
ea, nuestros ojos lo han visto.

81
00:03:16.550 --> 00:03:20.070
Tú lo has visto, oh, Jehová, no calles.

82
00:03:20.470 --> 00:03:21.110
Señor,

83
00:03:21.270 --> 00:03:22.950
