101
00:04:01.295 --> 00:04:02.495
y digan siempre,

102
00:04:02.974 --> 00:04:04.495
sea ensalzado

103
00:04:04.495 --> 00:04:05.375
Jehová,

104
00:04:05.535 --> 00:04:07.695
que ama la paz de su siervo,

105
00:04:08.175 --> 00:04:10.815
